    <title>重学前端-第3天</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2019/07/19/%E9%87%8D%E5%AD%A6%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF-%E7%AC%AC3%E5%A4%A9/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2019/07/19/重学前端-第3天/</id>
    <published>2019-07-19T02:10:01.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-07-19T09:42:16.029Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>注意点：<br>pc端图片最好不要超过200kb<br>尽量少使用通配符选择器</p><a id="more"></a><h3 id="引入ico图标"><a href="#引入ico图标" class="headerlink" title="引入ico图标"></a>引入ico图标</h3><p>favicon.ico</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;link rel=&quot;shortcut icon&quot; href=&quot;favicon.ico&quot; type=&quot;image/x-icon&quot; /&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>http://www.bitbug.net/</code> 制作ico图标</p><h3 id="网站优化3大标签"><a href="#网站优化3大标签" class="headerlink" title="网站优化3大标签"></a>网站优化3大标签</h3><p>seo 搜索引擎优化<br>title google 不允许超过35个中文 百度不允许超过28个中文  推荐： 网站名+网站描述<br>description 不超过120字<br>keyword 限制了6到8个关键词</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;title&gt;Document&lt;/title&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;meta name=&quot;description&quot; content=&quot;&quot; &gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;meta name=&quot;keyword&quot; content=&quot;&quot; &gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="字体图标"><a href="#字体图标" class="headerlink" title="字体图标"></a>字体图标</h3><p>几乎支持所有的浏览器，体积比图片更小，移动端首选；</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@font-face &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    font-family: &apos;icomoon&apos;;</span><br><span class="line">    src: url(&quot;fonts/icomoon.eot&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">    src: url(&quot;fonts/icomoon.eot&quot;) format(&quot;embedded-opentype&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">    src: url(&quot;fonts/icomoon.ttf&quot;) format(&quot;truetype&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">    src: url(&quot;fonts/icomoon.woff&quot;) format(&quot;woff&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">    src: url(&quot;fonts/icomoon.svg&quot;) format(&quot;svg&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">    font-weight: normal;</span><br><span class="line">    font-style: normal;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">div &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    font-family: &quot;icomoon&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="优化"><a href="#优化" class="headerlink" title="优化"></a>优化</h3><p>1、logo优化<br>添加背景图 h1 标签<br>h1 内包含a标签<br>在a标签内添加文字，添加背景，告诉搜索引擎；（text-indent: -9999px;或者 font-size: 0;）</p>]]></content>
    
